        "list_XffmV4": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_240648346.png",
            "heading": "1. It Prevents Stains Before They Form (So You Finally Stop Scrubbing)",
            "text": "<p><strong>Here's the problem with everything you've tried: </strong>bleach, pumice stones, expensive cleaners — they all attack stains after they form. <strong>You scrub. It comes back in 3 days. You scrub again.</strong><br/><br/>TrueClean releases a cleaning solution with every single flush — before new minerals stick to your bowl. <br/><br/><strong>No bond. No stain. No scrubbing.</strong></p>",
