            "heading": "2. It Actually Works on Hard Water (Unlike Everything Else)",
            "text": "<p>If you live in CA, AZ, TX, DC, or FL — you know what I’m talking about.<br/><br/>Those stubborn brown rings. The rust-colored streaks. The crusty mineral buildup that mock you and your scrub brush.<br/><br/>TrueClean's chlorine-based formula was engineered to break down and disperse hard water minerals so those ugly brown rings never form to begin with.</p>",
