            "heading": "4. Stop Scrubbing Every Week",
            "text": "<p>How many hours have you spent scrubbing toilets over the years?<br/><br/>I was scrubbing my toilet every week. I used to ruin so many toilet brushes because I'd have to scrub and scrub and scrub until the bristles were totally brown.<br/><br/>That's over now.</p>",
