            "text": "<p>I grew sick of being embarrassed by surprise guests who wanted to use the toilet— it would look like I went months between cleanings. REALLY gross!<br/><br/>With TrueClean, my toilet stays spotless on autopilot. No rings. No stains. No panic attack when the doorbell rings.</p>",
